{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58ee9259ab","title":"妇女工作者应参加经济工作","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0f978a12fe","index":0,"year":1943,"month":2,"day":24,"articleId":"58ee9259ab"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"38885a8fd9","type":"paragraph","text":"妇女工作者应参加经济工作","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"58ee9259ab"},{"id":"4f8e48d49d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1943年2月24日）妇女工作者本身必须学习农村经济知识，了解妇女生产内容才能真正成为农村群众生产的组织者与领导者。许多有能力的女同志必须到合作社去工作。再则许多女党员、女干部必须到公营经济机关中去工作，便公营经济发展起来。那些浮在上层、空网无事不以为耻，反以为荣的观点是完全错误的。H这是毛泽东在审园《中共中央关于各花日根据地目前妇女工作方针","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"58ee9259ab"}],"page":{"id":"ee0ce8280e","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"58ee9259ab","start":516,"end":516}}}},"__N_SSG":true}